description: Give your frame the protection it deserves. These grippy honeycomb panels are easy to apply and super durable.Durable 380 micron PVC protects your frame from scoring, with gripped texture.Semi-rigid, non-yellowing and UV-resistant.1 large piece for the downtube.4 chevrons for the down or top tube.4 parts for the chainstay.1 rectangle for custom use.Fits most trail, enduro, DH and all-mountain frames.
name: ALL MOUNTAIN STYLE Honeycomb Frame Guard Extra
